snippet.title: Psychonauts 2 - The Motherlobe Edition: Announce Trailer
snippet.description: In this collectible, physical edition of the much anticipated, Psychonauts 2 - The Motherlobe Edition, get the platform-adventure game and then some!  Packed in the game are quirky missions and mysterious conspiracies with cinematic style and tons of customizable psychic powers. The game pack-ins include exclusive stickers, art cards, a reversible coversheet AND a digital download code for behind the scenes footage.
